projects.name: Admin UI
projects.description: Creating an interface for admins to see, edit, and delete the users data. Created a webpage to display all the users data. Extracted the users data from API.

projects.name: Netflix Clone
projects.description: This is clone of Netflix website built using React as a Front-end & Firebase as Back-end. It contains the home page, sign-up page, sign-in page, and profile page. In this Netflix Clone movies data fetched using TMDb API. It has one feature that is user can sign-up and login & user can like their favourite movie.

projects.name: Ecommerce Website
projects.description: Ecommerce Website made using React, Tailwind CSS as Front-end & Strapi as Back-end. Payment gateway Feature is available in this website. It Contains the home page, category page, product details page. In this website you can add product and search any product.
